    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and has had the critical rod bearing service and valve clearances performed within the last 5,000 miles. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts crisply, paired with a refreshed subframe to address common chassis fatigue points. It retains its factory M-Variable Differential Lock for superior power delivery. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the suspension geometry is precise, currently running a Bilstein B16 coilover setup that enhances the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear architecture. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car with documented maintenance history.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
