      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan presents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor stone chips on the hood from normal highway driving. The interior is exceptionally clean, featuring smoke-free leather seats with minimal bolster wear and a fully functional suite of electronics, including the premium sound system and navigation. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a complete service log showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of brake pads and a cooling system flush. The tires offer plenty of tread for several seasons to come. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been cared for with pride.",
      "price": 31500.0,
